Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.46,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H171621&\3c&HFFFDFF&\fs110\bord5\an7\pos(184,558)\fad(180,500)}（子彈只裝了10發）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我的第一個問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一 那是能摸到的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:41.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,YES 並不是言語或概念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,二 那是電器產品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:44.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:48.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,三 那是溫暖或冰冷的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:49.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,YES
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,由剛才的回答能推出的結論有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:57.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,生物 食物 或是像熱水及冰那樣的物質
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,又亦或是營火或能調節溫度的器具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:01.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:06.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在有多了解四宮這個測試的前提下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:09.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,答案一定是與四宮輝夜有關的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:11.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四 它是四宮的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:20.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,五 是四宮今天觸碰過的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:21.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:24.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,六 四宮家有這個東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,連續三個NO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:32.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,本來以為是四宮的某樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,現在完全沒有頭緒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,再從四宮的心理找找線索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:38.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那就
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,七 是四宮喜歡的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？這個表情是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:56.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有一點害羞 難為情的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:58.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:05.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,八 那是生物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,YES
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微冷靜點 再確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可以摸得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是電子產品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是常溫的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是四宮的所有物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有碰過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,當然也不在四宮家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,符合條件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一個 是四宮喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:37.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:39.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,委婉的告白！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:41.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:45.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,九 是哪種喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友之間的 還是作為一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是其他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:57.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有答案 因為沒辦法用YES或NO回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:58.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太著急 浪費子彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:01.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:04.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還有可能是其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 十
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:15.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是非常聰明 帥氣 頭髮的顏色有點鮮艷 眸若清泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:27.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:32.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 絕對是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼彆扭的愛的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:42.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來 真是發生了很多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:46.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 每次都對四宮有新認識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:51.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:59.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 問題都問完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:08.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在某種程度上我很了解四宮這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:11.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮每次這樣的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:12.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:16.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,正確
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,準確的說應該是藤原書記養的佩斯
